1. Rate per night for the additional bed is unreasonably high.  The price is almost a standard room price;
2. Long waiting for the grab due to heavy traffic;

1. The bell man, all are friendly and helpful;
2. The distant to KLCC tower is good for the mid-aged individuals;
3. Couples of cafes & restaurants open early for a quick breakfast with varieties of food choices;
Stayed in March 2019
